    public class BranchImpl
extends ExtensionElementImpl
implements Branch
    An implementation of the model object 'Branch'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Circuit Number
    • From Side Metered
    • Original Branch Id
    • To Bus
    • From Bus
    • Network
